snippet.title: Atari Lynx Collection 2 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Recorded directly off the Evercade VS. This cart is focused around games that were developed by Epyx, who worked on the Lynx handheld itself.

Games:
00:07 - Blue Lightning
02:47 - California Games
07:28 - Checkered Flag
09:58 - Chip's Challenge
13:13 - Electrocop
20:06 - Gates of Zendocon
23:06 - Todd's Adventures in Slime World
27:30 - Zarlor Mercenary
